v1"><span begin="17.802" end="18.073">い</span><span begin="18.073" end="18.330">つ</span><span begin="18.330" end="18.602">も</span><span begin="18.602" end="19.354">通</span><span begin="19.354" end="19.557">り</span><span begin="19.557" end="19.768">可</span><span begin="19.768" end="20.019">愛</span><span begin="20.019" end="20.512">い</span><span begin="20.512" end="20.753">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">和往常一样可爱呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">itsumo doori kawaii yo</span></p><p begin="20.753" end="22.760" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.753" end="20.973">ダ</span><span begin="20.973" end="21.261">メ</span><span begin="21.261" end="21.492">ダ</span><span begin="21.492" end="21.734">メ！</span><span begin="21.972" end="22.442">だ</span><span begin="22.442" end="22.760">ね！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不行不行！ 就是啊！</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dame dame da ne</span></p><p begin="22.925" end="25.351" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="22.925" end="23.462">こ</span><span begin="23.462" end="23.959">ん</span><span begin="23.959" end="24.419">なん</span><span begin="24.419" end="24.872">じゃ</span> <span begin="24.872" end="25.351">「NO」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这样可不行 “NO”</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">konnan ja NO</span></p><p begin="25.582" end="28.711" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.582" end="26.090">とっ</span><span begin="26.090" end="26.321">て</span><span begin="26.321" end="26.811">お</span><span begin="26.811" end="27.030">き</span><span begin="27.030" end="27.280">が</span><span begin="27.280" end="27.531">い</span><span begin="27.531" end="27.761">い</span><span begin="27.761" end="28.232">な</span><span begin="28.232" end="28.711">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果想要珍藏的东西</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">totte oki ga ii nara</span></p><p begin="29.520" end="32.613" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.520" end="29.991">皆</span><span begin="29.991" end="30.212">に</span><span begin="30.212" end="30.700">魔</span><span begin="30.700" end="31.190">法</span><span begin="31.190" end="31.420">か</span><span begin="31.420" end="31.722">け</span><span begin="31.722" end="32.131">ま</span><span begin="32.131" end="32.613">しょう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就对大家施放魔法吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mina ni mahou kakemashou</span></p><p begin="33.471" end="36.410" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.471" end="33.900">嘘</span><span begin="33.900" end="34.132">み</span><span begin="34.132" end="34.461">た</span><span begin="34.461" end="34.630">い</span><span begin="34.630" end="34.960">な</span><span begin="34.960" end="35.152">ト</span><span begin="35.152" end="35.679">リッ</span><span begin="35.679" end="36.120">ク</span><span begin="36.120" end="36.410">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将如同梦幻一般的戏法</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">uso mitai na torikku o</span></p><p begin="36.612" end="40.339" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.612" end="37.060">衣</span><span begin="37.060" end="37.338">装</span><span begin="37.550" end="38.018">に</span><span begin="38.018" end="38.430">仕</span><span begin="38.618" end="39.039">掛</span><span begin="39.039" end="39.518">け</span><span begin="39.518" end="39.788">て</span><span begin="39.788" end="40.020">る</span><span begin="40.020" end="40.339">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在衣服上布置开吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ishou ni shikaketeru no</span></p><p begin="40.411" end="44.200" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.411" end="41.389">糸</span><span begin="42.229" end="42.718">一</span><span begin="42.718" end="42.959">つ</span><span begin="42.959" end="43.171">ほ</span><span begin="43.171" end="43.388">ど</span><span begin="43.388" end="43.838">け</span><span begin="43.838" end="44.200">ば</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只要解开一根丝线</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ito hitotsu hodokeba</span></p><p begin="44.400" end="47.991" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.400" end="45.875">全</span><span begin="46.166" end="46.636">身</span><span begin="46.636" end="46.865">が</span><span begin="46.865" end="47.295">キ</span><span begin="47.295" end="47.536">ラ</span><span begin="47.536" end="47.736">キ</span><span begin="47.736" end="47.991">ラ！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">全身就会闪闪发光！</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zenshin ga kirakira</span></p><p begin="48.307" end="50.216" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.307" end="48.817">メイ</span><span begin="48.817" end="49.205">キャップ！</span><span begin="49.308" end="49.808">ドレ</span><span begin="49.808" end="50.216">スアップ！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">Make up! Dress up!</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mei kyappu dore suappu</span></p><p begin="50.255" end="52.055" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.255" end="50.766">キュー</span><span begin="50.766" end="50.995">ト</span><span begin="50.995" end="51.204">に</span><span begin="51.204" end="51.693">RE:</span><span begin="51.693" end="52.055">BORN</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可爱地 RE:BORN</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">kyuu to ni ri boon</span></p><p begin="52.464" end="54.689" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.464" end="52.693">マ</span><span begin="52.693" end="52.926">ジ</span><span begin="52.926" end="53.092">カ</span><span begin="53.092" end="53.445">ル</span><span begin="53.445" end="53.695">ト</span><span begin="53.695" end="54.014">リッ</span><span begin="54.014" end="54.415">ク</span><span begin="54.415" end="54.689">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">用这神奇的戏法</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">majikaru torikku de</span></p><p begin="54.689" end="55.958" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.689" end="55.114">チェイン</span><span begin="55.114" end="55.547">チェイン</span><span begin="55.547" end="55.958">Change!</span><span ttm:role="x-tr