 begin="1:50.722" end="1:51.212">もっ</span><span begin="1:51.212" end="1:52.243">と</span><span begin="1:52.544" end="1:52.953">想</span><span begin="1:52.953" end="1:53.189">い</span><span begin="1:53.189" end="1:53.432">込</span><span begin="1:53.432" end="1:53.644">め</span><span begin="1:53.644" end="1:54.142">た</span><span begin="1:54.142" end="1:54.461">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果倾注更多心意的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">motto omoikometara</span></p><p begin="1:54.684" end="1:58.264" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.684" end="1:55.141">ス</span><span begin="1:55.141" end="1:56.369">テ</span><span begin="1:56.369" end="1:56.624">ー</span><span begin="1:56.624" end="1:56.874">ジ</span><span begin="1:56.874" end="1:57.103">も</span><span begin="1:57.103" end="1:57.544">キ</span><span begin="1:57.544" end="1:57.794">ラ</span><span begin="1:57.794" end="1:58.011">キ</span><span begin="1:58.011" end="1:58.264">ラ！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就连舞台也会闪闪发光！</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">suteeji mo kirakira</span></p><p begin="1:58.520" end="2:00.334" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:58.520" end="1:59.053">ペー</span><span begin="1:59.053" end="1:59.376">スアップ！</span><span begin="1:59.564" end="2:00.011">ドレ</span><span begin="2:00.011" end="2:00.334">スアップ！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">Pace up! Dress up!</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">pee suappu dore suappu</span></p><p begin="2:00.462" end="2:02.362" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.462" end="2:00.729">モ</span><span begin="2:00.729" end="2:00.972">ア</span><span begin="2:00.972" end="2:01.204">モ</span><span begin="2:01.204" end="2:01.433">ア</span> <span begin="2:01.433" end="2:01.912">RE:</span><span begin="2:01.912" end="2:02.362">BORN</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">More more RE:BORN</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">moa moa ri boon</span></p><p begin="2:02.684" end="2:04.918" itunes:key="L35